{"tid":1804440,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"武漢出現不明原因肺炎個案 惹重現沙士憂慮","createTime":"2019-12-31T03:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T05:42:39.000Z","uid":216992,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b3359f9de028c6410f2891b8d16192db8f82769e","tid":1804440,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"武漢出現不明原因肺炎個案　惹重現沙士憂慮<br />\n<br />\n武漢部分醫療機構出現不明原因的肺炎個案，當局已經對患者採取隔離措施，並表示將第一時間公布檢測結果。央視報道，國家衛健委專家組上午抵達武漢，展開相關檢測核實工作。武漢市衛生健康委員會日前發公告，說武漢市華南海鮮市場陸續出現不明原因肺炎，要求各醫療機構及時追蹤統計救治情況，並按要求及時上報。武漢疾控部門正前往救治醫院採集患者樣本。有報道引述上海市同濟大學的消息說，今次武漢肺炎病原體與俗稱沙士的「非典型肺炎」，同屬冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-31 11:42:14"},{"pid":"4823d7854a9b3d2b5673b2e30532cb9cda79495b","tid":1804440,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"即係真架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d3fedc143a1bf5c2f1edd12dde0a4f5fd6203a","tid":1804440,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好野"},{"pid":"8122b33237787dca440f5ab2a5e0bbb360429c9b","tid":1804440,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"咪撚傳過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0960fc69bb699e6c68f685d85058a9024f8d2329","tid":1804440,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"來來來"},{"pid":"1fb9b163b7845c16bd2d85a6940d9446daca7d51","tid":1804440,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8122b33237787dca440f5a